//]]&gt;
</script>"},{"type":"text/html","content":"<div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?v=1012500171080" data-width="466"><div class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?v=1012500171080">Post</a> by <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Manischewitz">Man-O-Manischewitz</a>.</div></div>"},{"type":"text/html","content":"<p><strong>That little &quot;K&quot; (<a href="http://www.kosherquest.org/symbols.php">along with its friends &quot;OU&quot; and &quot;P&quot;</a>); has been showing up beyond bottles of Manischewitz. Check out some of the (bizarre) ways companies try to leverage &quot;Kosher&quot;:</strong></p>"},{"type":"text/html","content":"<p>Coors claims to be &quot;<a href="http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-8890086.html" target="_blank">America’s First Kosher Beer</a>&quot; <a href="http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-8890086.html"></a></p>"},{"type":"text/html","content":"<p><a href="http://www.aksafaris.com/" target="_blank">Go on a Kosher Safari in Africa!</a> <a href="http://www.aksafaris.com/"></a></p>"},{"content":"<p><a href="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1641000041/making-an-award-winning-aged-cheddar-cheese-kosher" target="_blank">Kickstarter funded high-end Kosher cheese! </a><a href="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1641000041/making-an-award-winning-aged-cheddar-cheese-kosher"></a></p>","type":"text/html"},{"content":"<p>For a truly hands on experience: <a href="http://www.kosherfest.com/" target="_blank">Get yourself a ticket to Kosherfest</a>. <a href="http://www.kosherfest.com/"></a></p>","type":"text/html"}]
